[thinking] **Examining dynamic class loading**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I just realized that Janino compiles to bytecode, but when it comes to the native image, dynamic class loading isn't supported. That makes me think that existing tests might include NativeImageDynamicClassLoadingSupport, and perhaps we need to skip those tests. I feel like it's important to inspect the situation further to ensure everything is working correctly. I'll dig into this to understand the implications better!
