ther than missing setup.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"Janino 3.1.0 still depends transitively on org.codehaus.janino:commons-compiler:3.1.0. The old org.codehaus.janino.util.iterator.Iterables class is no longer in the janino jar; the equivalent utility is in org.codehaus.commons.compiler.util.iterator.Iterables from the transitive commons-compiler jar. Prefer tests of public Janino APIs such as ExpressionEvaluator, ScriptEvaluator, ClassBodyEvaluator, SimpleCompiler, and Compiler. No environment variables or system properties are required.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Do not add org.apache.ant:ant unless deliberately testing Janino's optional Ant integration; it is optional/provided in the POM and not needed for meaningful core coverage.\",\n    \"Some Janino scenarios generate and load classes dynamically, which can be limited under native image; tests should preserve the existing native-image-aware handling rather than treating every generated-class loading failure as a setup problem.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_04acefc1fde32f01016a42c340921c8194b1112f2474c70eb5\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 900, "output": 785, "cacheRead": 24064, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 25749, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782760246433, "responseId": "resp_04acefc1fde32f01016a42c33719048194b0d13ab78f28f650"}, "toolResults": []}
